comments.body:
Non-privileged container configuration can refer to #1011.
It is a follow-up to #1012. I think that although the container cannot be run in a non-privileged container, this should only be for the `run` command and should not be directed to other commands. Other `buildah` commands should be executed normally.
@rhatdan @TomSweeneyRedHat @giuseppe @nalind @umohnani8 PTAL
